  "title": "PRODUCTION TECHNICIAN - GERMAN MNC (LOYANG)",
  "description": "<p><strong>• German MNC</strong><br /><strong>• Salary: Up to $3,000 Basic + OT allowances + Variable Bonuses</strong><br /><strong>• 5-day week Monday to Friday, office hours 9 am to 6pm</strong><br /><strong>• Working location: Loyang</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Manufacturing of chemical products in accordance with the weekly production schedule</p></li><li><p>Ensuring availability of all raw materials and packing materials before commencement of weekly production</p></li><li><p>Ensuring all raw materials are correctly identified and accounted for</p></li><li><p>Maintain housekeeping in the production and area in accordance with the ISO, EHS for Safety and other Governance requirement.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li><p>At least N/O level</p></li><li><p>Nitec in Chemical process or equivalent will have advantage</p></li><li><p>Required to Wear Personal Protective Equipment as per company policy</p></li><li><p>Experience with Chemical production will have advantage</p></li></ul><p><br />All Successful candidates can expect a very competitive remuneration package and a comprehensive range of benefits.<br /></p><p>Kindly email your resume in a detailed Word format to<br /></p><p><a href=\"mailto:roy.yeo@peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>roy.yeo@peopleprofilers.com</strong></a><br /></p><p>People Profilers Pte Ltd</p><p>20 Cecil Street, #08-09 PLUS Building Singapore 049705</p><p>EA License Number: 02C4944</p><p>Registration Number: R1217882</p><p>Posting Personnel: Yeo Yi Rong</p><p>Tel:  <a href=\"tel:65 6950 9757\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">65 6950 9757</a></p>",
